definition: Hmong or Miao ethnic group of southwest China/surname Miao

sentences.english: The seedlings were placed in a big flat.
sentences.chinese: 秧苗被放置在一大片浅苗床上。

sentences.english: They treat their seeds with a fungicide to combat seedling diseases.
sentences.chinese: 真菌剂浸泡种子来防止秧苗受病。

sentences.english: The farmers are bedding up for planting seedlings.
sentences.chinese: 农民们为栽秧苗翻地作垄。

sentences.english: The farmer bedded the seedlings in.
sentences.chinese: 农民把秧苗栽在苗圃里。

sentences.english: Seedling perpendicularity is one of the most important targets of evaluating transplant machine performance.
sentences.chinese: 秧苗直立度是评价移栽机性能重要指标之一。

sentences.english: The seedlings need to grow partially submerged.
sentences.chinese: 秧苗要部分浸水才能种植。

sentences.english: Seedbed soil fertilizing is one of the key measures for raising mechanical transplanting rice seedling.
sentences.chinese: 床土培肥是培育水稻机插秧苗的首要措施。

sentences.english: Medicament regulation can control over growth of seedlings and improve seedling quality.
sentences.chinese: 采用药剂调控可显著控制幼苗徒长，提高秧苗素质。

sentences.english: In the meantime, there are obvious effects to the viability and quality of rice seedlings.
sentences.chinese: 而且对提高田间成秧率与秧苗素质都有明显的效果。

sentences.english: The rice seedling arranging machine is a new type of transplanter that is suitable to the carpet seedlings.
sentences.chinese: 水稻摆秧机是一种适宜于移栽毯状秧苗的浅植机械。

sentences.english: There was no significant difference in senescene between DRS and PRS .
sentences.chinese: 而肥床旱育和塑盘旱育秧苗没有明显差异。

sentences.english: Keep the seedlings moist, but not too wet, otherwise the roots will rot.
sentences.chinese: 让秧苗保持湿润，但是浇水不要太多，否则会烂根。

sentences.english: Put seedlings into the mud and the roots of seedlings in the mud and then seal the real thing.
sentences.chinese: 要把秧苗放进泥里，再用泥把秧的根部封实一点。

sentences.english: In the fields we met a group of girls working on tomato plants.
sentences.chinese: 在地里，我们看到一群姑娘在管理西红柿秧苗。

sentences.english: The rice seedlings were covered with plastic sheeting.
sentences.chinese: 秧苗上面覆盖着塑料薄膜。

sentences.english: This explained in character of rice why technology of growing rice seedling in bottle could increase yield.
sentences.chinese: 从秧苗素质角度解释了水稻钵苗摆栽技术的增产机理。

definition: to sprout/to come out (of seedling)/to bud
tiller (stem at the base of grass plants)
(of plants) to turn green again/to revegetate
